50|$|Many amateur-satellites {{receive an}} OSCAR {{designation}}, {{which is an}} acronym for Orbiting <b>Satellite</b> Carrying <b>Amateur</b> Radio. The designation is assigned by AMSAT, an organization which promotes the development and launch of <b>amateur</b> radio <b>satellites.</b> Because of the prevalence of this designation, <b>amateur</b> radio <b>satellites</b> are {{often referred to as}} OSCARs.|$|R
